---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Career Development - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- HERO WITH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507679799987-c73779587ccf?w=1920&q=80"
    alt="Career growth"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900/90 via-emerald-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <p class="text-emerald-300 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
      People
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      Career<br/>Development
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      About two-thirds of our waking hours are devoted to work. Wisely choosing our career path is an important element for healthy mental and emotional lives.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 py-10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center text-white">
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold">8</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-emerald-100">Careers per Lifetime</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold">67%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-emerald-100">Waking Hours at Work</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold">100+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-emerald-100">Clients Guided</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold">95%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-emerald-100">Satisfaction Rate</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SLIDING DOORS -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Reality</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Sliding Doors</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          It wasn't so long ago that people believed they should have a job for life. The common view was "Till death do us apart."
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          However, in today's fast-paced work environment, people are expected on average to hold <strong>eight different careers</strong> over their lifetime.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Like any change, career development involves a gradual growth process. Success is achieved when an appropriate career path is formulatedâ€”one that embodies potential for employment realization, increases satisfaction, and meets personal, social, and economic needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-3xl p-8 text-white h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">Our Insight</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-100 leading-relaxed">
            Individuals tend to choose their professional path as a reflection of how they see themselves and the place they think they are entitled.
          </p>
          <p class="text-emerald-100 leading-relaxed mt-4 font-semibold">
            Our job is to empower our consultees and enhance their sense of security and competence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR OFFERING -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-emerald-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Process</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Offering</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Deep Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We analyze strengths, desires and needs. We dive into your value system, abilities, skills, and experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Gap Discovery</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We uncover and discuss gaps between your current employment state and future expectations.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Clear Picture</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          After clarifying the full picture, we understand exactly where you are and where you want to be.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Practical Plan</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We formulate a practical work plan for bridging these gaps and achieving your career goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />
</Layout>
